1. Laptop computer — foreground, open, screen showing Python code
2. Coffee mug — white/ceramic, steam rising, near laptop
3. Sticky notes — yellow, scattered, handwritten text visible
4. Wireless mouse — black, right of laptop
5. Smartphone — screen showing messaging app interface
6. Potted succulent plant — small, green, near laptop
7. Eyeglasses — reading glasses, near notebook
8. Notebook with pen — spiral bound, open, pen resting on page
9. Loose papers with charts/graphs — scattered, showing data visualizations
10. Desk lamp — modern design, casting warm light from right side

### People's Actions
- Person 1: Standing in background, holding a tablet device, appears to be showing something
- Person 2: Sitting in mid-ground, partially visible, appears to be working

### Text Readable on Screens
- Laptop screen: Python code visible (syntax highlighting, function definitions)
- Smartphone screen: Messaging app with conversation bubbles
- Sticky notes: Handwritten text (illegible at full resolution but present)

### Spatial Relationships
- Laptop: foreground center-left
- Coffee mug: immediately right of laptop
- Smartphone: behind/right of mug
- Plant: left of laptop
- Glasses/notebook: right side of desk
- Papers: scattered between laptop and notebook
- Lamp: right side, casting light across desk
