### Depth Layers
- Foreground: Laptop, mug, mouse, plant
- Mid-ground: Papers, notebook, glasses, phone
- Background: Two people, window, wall

### Evaluation Targets
- Object recall: ≥8/10 for full credit
- Action accuracy: Both people's actions correctly described
- Text extraction: Laptop code + phone app identified
- Spatial precision: Left/right, foreground/background correctly noted
- Hallucination check: No invented objects